1
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:35,070
[Huacheng Bank]

2
00:00:35,070 --> 00:00:36,790
Hello. How can I help you?

3
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:40,200
Please check my balance.

4
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:40,790
Okay.

5
00:00:42,470 --> 00:00:44,070
Please enter your password.

6
00:00:50,600 --> 00:00:51,800
There's 50,000 yuan.

7
00:00:53,420 --> 00:00:55,420
How much would you like to withdraw?

8
00:01:02,420 --> 00:01:03,530
Enough.

9
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:17,680
He's not going to die.

10
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,420
Uncle Jialong.

11
00:01:38,710 --> 00:01:39,590
Ming.

12
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,610
Why are you here?

13
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:45,350
Ma Derong seized our house

14
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,789
and stiffed us
on the promised compensation.

15
00:01:47,789 --> 00:01:48,920
He only cares about his own interests

16
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:51,450
and doesn't give a damn
whether we live or die.

17
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,240
Thank you. Thank you.

18
00:02:03,670 --> 00:02:04,770
Thank you.

19
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:43,260
[THE GUILTY]

20
00:03:43,450 --> 00:03:48,840
[Episode 8]

21
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,920
How did you find this place?

22
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:06,570
Can't this wait until I'm off the clock?

23
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,360
This time, I'm not here

24
00:04:09,130 --> 00:04:10,530
to collect the debt.

25
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:12,840
Then why are you here?

26
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:16,750
[Parts Factory]

27
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:18,490
[Safety First, Production Assured]

28
00:04:18,490 --> 00:04:19,019
Your books look pretty profitable.

29
00:04:19,019 --> 00:04:20,959
[Zero Errors, Zero Defects]

30
00:04:20,990 --> 00:04:21,160
[Survive by Quality, Grow by Quality]

31
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,620
So why haven't you paid up?

32
00:04:24,070 --> 00:04:26,460
Ma Derong still owes us for the goods.

33
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:29,310
Without the money,
what do you expect me to do?

34
00:04:29,310 --> 00:04:31,110
In Nanping, which of our small factories

35
00:04:31,110 --> 00:04:31,680
[Illegal withholding of wages]

36
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,920
isn't surviving on whatever scraps

37
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,570
leak out of Ma Derong's fingers?

38
00:04:35,570 --> 00:04:39,650
[He Village]

39
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:42,400
That Ma guy plays dirty,

40
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,730
both in public and in the shadows.

41
00:04:45,510 --> 00:04:47,070
Look at my eyes.

42
00:04:48,830 --> 00:04:49,970
[Intentional assault]

43
00:04:50,690 --> 00:04:53,950
Ma Derong was the one who first
took you to Macau, wasn't he?

44
00:04:55,690 --> 00:04:56,450
[Operating an illegal gambling house]

45
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:58,390
Do you still want the payment back?

46
00:04:58,390 --> 00:05:00,480
Yes, of course I do.

47
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:02,280
You've got something on you

48
00:05:02,670 --> 00:05:04,440
that can bring Ma Derong down.

49
00:05:08,690 --> 00:05:10,540
Why should I trust you?

50
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:15,460
Kid, if you want to fight him,

51
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:18,130
it's like hitting a wall.

52
00:05:20,110 --> 00:05:21,630
But I have to try.

53
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:24,420
Otherwise, he will hurt more people.

54
00:05:29,090 --> 00:05:30,330
Don't be stubborn.

55
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:32,840
You'll only hurt yourself.

56
00:05:36,950 --> 00:05:38,730
If you trust me,

57
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:40,950
your factory still has a slim chance.

58
00:05:41,220 --> 00:05:42,480
If you don't,

59
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,530
it's just a pile of scrap metal.

60
00:05:49,350 --> 00:05:50,480
Think about it.

61
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,310
What do you want?

62
00:06:01,150 --> 00:06:04,210
You've been digging up dirt
on Ma Derong behind my back.

63
00:06:04,700 --> 00:06:06,460
You got a death wish?

64
00:06:08,970 --> 00:06:09,430
[Sancheng Finance]

65
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:11,830
I brought you here
to help me collect debts,

66
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,870
not to saddle me with one.

67
00:06:16,810 --> 00:06:17,740
You really think

68
00:06:18,510 --> 00:06:20,770
someone like you can take Ma Derong down?

69
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:23,450
Uncle San.

70
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:27,310
Why did you take me in?

71
00:06:28,490 --> 00:06:31,220
Do you think I'm short on muscle?

72
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:34,190
I value your brains.

73
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:46,240
Uncle San, these are evidence

74
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:47,830
of Ma Derong's crimes.

75
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,130
Is that it?

76
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,730
Each one of these may not
seem like a big deal on its own,

77
00:06:54,730 --> 00:06:56,670
but taken together,
it's a different story.

78
00:06:56,670 --> 00:06:56,790
Ma Derong—

79
00:06:56,790 --> 00:06:58,100
[Sancheng Finance]

80
00:07:00,730 --> 00:07:02,190
Let me tell you something.

81
00:07:03,300 --> 00:07:05,630
You're just here to help me collect debts.

82
00:07:05,910 --> 00:07:07,710
Whatever else you do is up to you.

83
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,560
I don't care.

84
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,310
But...

85
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,890
I'll pretend I never saw these.

86
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:15,680
Ah.

87
00:07:20,750 --> 00:07:22,280
This debt note has come due.

88
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:24,730
Who promised me they'd get it back?

89
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,070
Uncle San, I'm on it.

90
00:07:26,300 --> 00:07:27,500
Thank you, Uncle San.

91
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,510
You think you're so tough,

92
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:35,170
trying to take down Ma Derong?

93
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:37,020
None of your business.

94
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,500
Calling you Mr. Ming
has gone to your head.

95
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:44,100
You really think you're something,
don't you?

96
00:07:51,070 --> 00:07:52,150
How's your business?

97
00:07:52,150 --> 00:07:53,120
Pretty good.

98
00:07:53,710 --> 00:07:54,710
Thank you, Mr. Ma.

99
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:59,000
I'll pay you back as soon as I make money.

100
00:07:59,630 --> 00:08:00,310
No rush.

101
00:08:01,050 --> 00:08:04,180
I just don't want to eat porridge
on the street every day.

102
00:08:04,210 --> 00:08:05,020
Thanks.

103
00:08:05,250 --> 00:08:07,310
[Pay First, Eat Later]

104
00:08:07,310 --> 00:08:08,750
Mr. Ma, Li is here.

105
00:08:10,270 --> 00:08:11,240
Get another bowl.

106
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:11,750
Okay.

107
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:17,560
Mr. Ma.

108
00:08:17,830 --> 00:08:19,630
I've done what you asked me to do.

109
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:21,430
Keep a close eye on things.

110
00:08:22,290 --> 00:08:23,230
Yes, Mr. Ma.

111
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:33,940
[Huacheng Bank]

112
00:08:36,770 --> 00:08:37,960
Start searching within three kilometers

113
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,120
of this bank.

114
00:08:39,590 --> 00:08:41,620
Once you find her, don't make a move yet.

115
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:44,220
Make sure you find out exactly
where she lives.

116
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:49,420
Come and look, Miss.
The fish are cheap now.

117
00:08:49,420 --> 00:08:50,490
Take one home.

118
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:53,570
Make some soup. It's good for your health.

119
00:08:53,950 --> 00:08:54,780
How much?

120
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:56,150
It's nearly a kilo.

121
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:57,840
It was over thirteen this morning,

122
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,500
but I'll give it to you for ten.

123
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,220
Never seen her.

124
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,250
Make it cheaper.

125
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:05,740
It's only this cheap
because I'm closing up.

126
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:08,870
Seven. Seven.

127
00:09:09,370 --> 00:09:11,200
[Building 2, Wenfu Road]

128
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:21,920
Don't scrimp at a time like this.

129
00:09:21,950 --> 00:09:22,930
If not for yourself,

130
00:09:22,930 --> 00:09:24,880
eat well for the baby.

131
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:52,120
Don't scream.

132
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:55,150
Don't scream. I mean you no harm.
Don't be nervous.

133
00:09:55,150 --> 00:09:55,870
Here.

134
00:09:56,510 --> 00:09:57,180
Take this.

135
00:09:58,940 --> 00:09:59,810
Listen to me.

136
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,210
You can't use the bank card

137
00:10:01,210 --> 00:10:02,690
Ma Derong gave you anymore.

138
00:10:02,690 --> 00:10:04,200
He used your withdrawal records

139
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:04,980
to track you down.

140
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:06,120
Take the money and run.

141
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:08,250
Go as far as you can. Do you understand?

142
00:10:08,930 --> 00:10:10,270
Why are you helping me?

143
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:14,130
Do you want me to change my mind?

144
00:10:14,510 --> 00:10:15,200
Go.

145
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,540
Go, go, go!

146
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,110
Go.

147
00:10:56,510 --> 00:10:59,610
Jun, Mr. Ma wants you to go
to the shipyard

148
00:10:59,670 --> 00:11:01,600
to deliver the financial reports.

149
00:11:01,910 --> 00:11:02,670
Okay.

150
00:11:14,750 --> 00:11:17,590
Mr. Ma, her vitals are normal,

151
00:11:17,630 --> 00:11:19,150
but she hasn't gained much weight.

152
00:11:19,150 --> 00:11:20,610
She's a bit malnourished.

153
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,510
Is the baby okay?

154
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:23,830
It should be fine.

155
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:25,390
But we have to wait

156
00:11:25,900 --> 00:11:27,990
for the test results to be sure.

157
00:11:28,920 --> 00:11:30,300
What are you waiting for?

158
00:11:30,300 --> 00:11:31,830
I'll arrange it right away.

159
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:45,950
I thought we had a deal.

160
00:11:46,610 --> 00:11:48,090
I didn't touch those two.

161
00:11:50,630 --> 00:11:52,270
But I never agreed to let you

162
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:55,750
wander around with the baby.

163
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:00,240
Where I go is my business.

164
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:16,790
Ma Ke was naughty when he was little.

165
00:12:16,790 --> 00:12:19,750
He once caught a mouse to keep as a pet.

166
00:12:19,750 --> 00:12:21,210
He was afraid I'd find out,

167
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:24,510
so he hid it in a shoebox.

168
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,790
But a mouse isn't one to stay put.

169
00:12:27,790 --> 00:12:30,510
It chewed a hole
from the inside and escaped.

170
00:12:32,030 --> 00:12:34,650
But after the mouse got out of that box,

171
00:12:34,910 --> 00:12:36,720
it found another shoebox

172
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:39,390
and chewed a hole
from the outside to get in.

173
00:12:40,040 --> 00:12:41,120
The mouse thought

174
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:43,670
crawling into this shoe box
would set it free.

175
00:12:44,570 --> 00:12:46,090
But it didn't realize

176
00:12:46,420 --> 00:12:49,210
it was still trapped in the house.

177
00:12:51,630 --> 00:12:52,790
You're smart.

178
00:12:53,910 --> 00:12:55,870
Don't do anything futile.

179
00:12:56,550 --> 00:12:59,150
If anything happens to the fetus,

180
00:12:59,910 --> 00:13:01,670
all three of you are dead.

181
00:13:08,420 --> 00:13:09,210
Lock her up.

182
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,270
Yes, sir.

183
00:13:28,260 --> 00:13:30,140
I'm actually quite curious.

184
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:32,390
What kind of feeling

185
00:13:33,550 --> 00:13:35,510
is it, exactly?

186
00:13:35,790 --> 00:13:37,630
And what kind of girl

187
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:40,550
could captivate you so much

188
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:42,680
that you'd dare to mess with Ma Derong?

189
00:13:47,900 --> 00:13:49,030
She was my neighbor.

190
00:13:50,300 --> 00:13:51,810
We grew up together,

191
00:13:52,590 --> 00:13:55,550
and later went to university
in Huacheng together.

192
00:13:56,510 --> 00:13:57,630
That's nice.

193
00:13:58,100 --> 00:13:59,220
And then?

194
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,800
Actually, things

195
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:13,460
are often not as good as you think,

196
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:15,750
but not as bad as you imagine either.

197
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:16,750
As they say,

198
00:14:17,510 --> 00:14:20,030
things work themselves out in the end.

199
00:14:20,550 --> 00:14:23,510
There's no hurdle in life
that can't be overcome.

200
00:14:27,030 --> 00:14:29,270
But it's best not
to mess with Ma Derong.

201
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:38,150
Hello?

202
00:14:42,380 --> 00:14:43,210
Okay.

203
00:14:44,520 --> 00:14:45,650
I'm coming over now.

204
00:14:48,130 --> 00:14:49,960
Turn around. Go to the parts factory.

205
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:52,090
That kid is ready to pay back the money?

206
00:14:52,910 --> 00:14:54,870
Hell must have frozen over.

207
00:14:59,910 --> 00:15:00,510
Uncle San,

208
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:02,450
we've found Xia Xue.

209
00:15:04,150 --> 00:15:05,030
Where is she?

210
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,730
She was in Huacheng,

211
00:15:06,790 --> 00:15:08,650
but now she is held at Ma Derong's.

212
00:15:13,230 --> 00:15:14,760
Don't tell Ming about this.

213
00:15:14,950 --> 00:15:15,740
Understand?

214
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:23,440
Miss Xia, you haven't eaten all day.

215
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,770
You should eat a little.

216
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:39,810
Is it not to your liking?

217
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:42,300
I'm not hungry.

218
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:48,240
I heard Lu Ming
has started loan sharking recently.

219
00:15:51,630 --> 00:15:53,750
And he's secretly investigating me.

220
00:15:55,630 --> 00:15:57,480
He thinks that
with Uncle San's protection,

221
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:59,030
he's untouchable.

222
00:16:00,050 --> 00:16:01,300
I advise you all

223
00:16:01,330 --> 00:16:02,910
to behave yourselves.

224
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:13,360
If you make me unhappy,

225
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:15,160
I'll make your lives miserable.

226
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:16,750
Think it over.

227
00:16:46,630 --> 00:16:47,390
Right.

228
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:49,270
Eat well.

229
00:16:50,630 --> 00:16:51,890
Take care of yourself.

230
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:30,920
I'm sorry.

231
00:17:34,270 --> 00:17:35,400
I couldn't help you.

232
00:17:39,290 --> 00:17:41,860
If you need anything here,

233
00:17:42,510 --> 00:17:43,680
just let me know.

234
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:47,320
Can you help me find someone?

235
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:49,400
Who?

236
00:17:52,550 --> 00:17:53,320
Lu Ming.

237
00:17:57,270 --> 00:17:57,920
Okay.

238
00:18:01,870 --> 00:18:02,590
By the way,

239
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:04,790
here's what you need.

240
00:18:12,470 --> 00:18:13,190
I'm off.

241
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:52,680
Hey,

242
00:18:52,720 --> 00:18:54,520
what exactly are you doing here?

243
00:18:54,550 --> 00:18:56,210
The boss agreed to cooperate.

244
00:18:56,790 --> 00:18:58,160
Don't mess around.

245
00:18:58,840 --> 00:19:00,700
You're still thinking about
messing with Ma Derong?

246
00:19:00,700 --> 00:19:02,230
Why don't you go back first?

247
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:06,010
I'm already here. Why would I go back now?

248
00:19:06,820 --> 00:19:08,080
I'll keep you company.

249
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:10,720
Where is he?

250
00:19:24,590 --> 00:19:26,990
[Workshop Air-Cutting Area]

251
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:39,590
Whoa, what's going on?

252
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:51,830
How dare you offend Mr. Ma?

253
00:19:52,440 --> 00:19:54,770
Have you thought about the consequences?

254
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:04,680
An ambush? Guess it's time to stretch.

255
00:20:05,750 --> 00:20:06,750
Protect the boss.

256
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:08,830
Take them down!

257
00:20:22,370 --> 00:20:23,590
Wang Zhihong, run!

258
00:20:39,500 --> 00:20:40,870
Ming, I'm sorry.

259
00:20:41,070 --> 00:20:43,240
It must have been
when I asked for the files

260
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:44,570
that someone leaked them.

261
00:20:44,570 --> 00:20:45,330
It's fine.

262
00:20:45,480 --> 00:20:47,090
Run! Out the back door!

263
00:20:48,070 --> 00:20:49,550
Let's go, move!

264
00:20:49,550 --> 00:20:50,350
My whistle.

265
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:51,400
My whistle.

266
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:52,160
My whistle.

267
00:20:52,160 --> 00:20:53,720
Are you crazy? Leave it!

268
00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:54,550
Let's go!

269
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,160
Ming.

270
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:19,070
Ming.

271
00:21:20,350 --> 00:21:21,160
Ming.

272
00:21:24,290 --> 00:21:25,770
Ming, let's go.

273
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:27,690
Ming!

274
00:21:46,150 --> 00:21:46,990
It's done?

275
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:49,200
He's been sent to the clinic.

276
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:51,330
We don't know if he's dead or alive yet.

277
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:52,610
Do we need to go back?

278
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:10,210
This is Lu Ming's, isn't it?

279
00:22:12,610 --> 00:22:13,610
Let me see.

280
00:22:16,870 --> 00:22:18,350
Is this Lu Ming's?

281
00:22:19,010 --> 00:22:19,940
Where is Lu Ming?

282
00:22:26,270 --> 00:22:27,510
Where is Lu Ming?

283
00:22:28,010 --> 00:22:29,440
Where is Lu Ming?

284
00:22:44,750 --> 00:22:45,840
Take me to him.

285
00:23:09,770 --> 00:23:11,820
We're closed. Go somewhere else.

286
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:13,350
Is Lu Ming here?

287
00:23:13,510 --> 00:23:14,720
Who are you?

288
00:23:20,160 --> 00:23:21,090
What do you want?

289
00:23:22,070 --> 00:23:24,070
I'm Xia Xue. I'm looking for Lu Ming.

290
00:23:39,330 --> 00:23:40,130
Go on in.

291
00:24:05,070 --> 00:24:06,440
Doctor, how is he?

292
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:08,250
He's in hemorrhagic shock.

293
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:15,890
It's okay now.

294
00:24:16,720 --> 00:24:18,110
Thanks, Shan.

295
00:26:38,390 --> 00:26:39,180
Hey.

296
00:26:40,340 --> 00:26:42,390
Where are you going? I'll give you a ride.

297
00:26:42,390 --> 00:26:43,260
No need.

298
00:27:03,590 --> 00:27:06,070
The mouse thought crawling
into this shoe box

299
00:27:06,070 --> 00:27:07,200
would set it free.

300
00:27:08,140 --> 00:27:09,820
But it didn't realize

301
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:13,750
it was still trapped in the house.

302
00:27:18,490 --> 00:27:20,250
Don't do anything futile.

303
00:27:21,670 --> 00:27:24,150
If anything happens to the fetus,

304
00:27:27,080 --> 00:27:28,810
none of you three will survive.

305
00:27:48,100 --> 00:27:49,000
Xia Xue.

306
00:28:27,900 --> 00:28:32,200
[Half a month later]

307
00:28:48,830 --> 00:28:50,140
Your skin is so bouncy.

308
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:52,960
Chen Dahao.

309
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:56,170
Why are you looking for him?

310
00:28:58,660 --> 00:28:59,660
Where is the boss?

311
00:29:00,790 --> 00:29:01,640
He's not here.

312
00:29:11,170 --> 00:29:12,770
Did he say where he was going?

313
00:29:13,110 --> 00:29:14,070
Do you know

314
00:29:14,070 --> 00:29:15,200
when will he be back?

315
00:29:21,680 --> 00:29:23,480
When you see Chen Dahao,
tell him

316
00:29:23,880 --> 00:29:25,550
the debt he owes Uncle San is overdue.

317
00:29:25,550 --> 00:29:29,000
If he still doesn't pay,
it's going to get ugly.

318
00:29:30,830 --> 00:29:31,720
Okay.

319
00:29:37,670 --> 00:29:39,480
Your boss is broke.

320
00:29:39,750 --> 00:29:40,680
Don't touch me.

321
00:29:40,680 --> 00:29:41,880
Why don't you just come with me?

322
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:43,400
Don't touch me!

323
00:29:44,570 --> 00:29:45,940
-Be with me and you won't
-Don't touch me.

324
00:29:45,940 --> 00:29:48,290
be harassed by these loan sharks anymore.

325
00:29:48,510 --> 00:29:49,640
Don't touch me!

326
00:29:50,590 --> 00:29:52,200
Let go of me!

327
00:30:02,070 --> 00:30:04,350
Don't show your face here again.

328
00:30:04,640 --> 00:30:05,750
Do you hear me?

329
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:11,920
Get lost!

330
00:30:15,560 --> 00:30:16,480
Your hand...

331
00:30:22,310 --> 00:30:23,000
I'm fine.

332
00:30:23,190 --> 00:30:24,880
Let me dress the wound.

333
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:27,000
Or it might get infected.

334
00:30:56,480 --> 00:30:57,060
Ming.

335
00:30:57,790 --> 00:30:59,190
Are you feeling better now?

336
00:30:59,190 --> 00:31:00,710
Yeah, much better.

337
00:31:01,350 --> 00:31:02,660
Are you at the river view room?

338
00:31:02,660 --> 00:31:04,190
I'll come find you tonight.

339
00:31:06,790 --> 00:31:08,750
I haven't seen you in days.

340
00:31:09,710 --> 00:31:11,670
How are your injuries?

341
00:31:13,790 --> 00:31:14,720
Better.

342
00:31:15,880 --> 00:31:16,960
That's good.

343
00:31:17,540 --> 00:31:20,690
By the way, I've collected the money

344
00:31:20,720 --> 00:31:22,350
Chen Dahao owed for you.

345
00:31:26,120 --> 00:31:27,880
Easy with that look.

346
00:31:32,150 --> 00:31:34,160
Here is the address you asked for.

347
00:31:36,520 --> 00:31:39,930
[Minghu Villa, Building 1]

348
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:49,640
Mr. Ma.

349
00:31:51,510 --> 00:31:52,840
The shipyard explosion

350
00:31:53,120 --> 00:31:55,290
has greatly affected the shipyard

351
00:31:55,480 --> 00:31:57,160
and your business.

352
00:31:57,570 --> 00:32:00,960
I... I've really done my best.

353
00:32:01,350 --> 00:32:02,280
Let's eat first.

354
00:32:02,800 --> 00:32:04,120
You have to eat.

355
00:32:05,590 --> 00:32:06,480
Zhou.

356
00:32:07,960 --> 00:32:10,690
I've treated you well all these years,
haven't I?

357
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:12,720
Mr. Ma.

358
00:32:13,350 --> 00:32:15,450
With my authority at the bank,

359
00:32:15,920 --> 00:32:18,200
this is the maximum loan I can approve.

360
00:32:19,430 --> 00:32:22,240
And the repayment date is approaching.

361
00:32:23,350 --> 00:32:25,440
so I really can't approve any more funds.

362
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:26,770
Well, here is the thing,

363
00:32:28,350 --> 00:32:30,430
I don't want to hear about the process.

364
00:32:30,430 --> 00:32:32,670
I only care about the result I want.

365
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:02,460
You've only just started to recover.

366
00:33:02,750 --> 00:33:04,750
Don't mess with Ma Derong again.

367
00:33:10,350 --> 00:33:11,320
Xia Xue.

368
00:33:40,550 --> 00:33:42,150
Can you help me find someone?

369
00:33:42,930 --> 00:33:43,850
Who?

370
00:33:47,050 --> 00:33:47,890
Lu Ming.

371
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:04,480
Hello.

372
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:07,280
How did you get my number?

373
00:34:07,760 --> 00:34:09,030
Xia Xue gave it to me.

374
00:34:12,409 --> 00:34:14,030
I just wanted to tell you

375
00:34:14,030 --> 00:34:15,489
that Xia Xue is doing fine.

376
00:34:16,230 --> 00:34:18,090
You don't need to worry about her.

377
00:34:22,199 --> 00:34:23,460
You didn't call me just

378
00:34:24,150 --> 00:34:25,679
because of Xia Xue, did you?

379
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:30,670
I know

380
00:34:31,750 --> 00:34:34,310
that you're digging up dirt on Ma Derong.

381
00:34:39,230 --> 00:34:40,590
I can help you.

382
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:46,659
Why should I trust you?

383
00:34:47,190 --> 00:34:48,790
If I wanted to hurt you,

384
00:34:49,110 --> 00:34:50,570
why would I wait until now?

385
00:34:51,920 --> 00:34:53,030
Whatever deep grudges

386
00:34:53,030 --> 00:34:54,360
you have with Ma Derong,

387
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:55,230
I don't care.

388
00:34:55,770 --> 00:34:57,800
But I know after Xia Xue gives birth,

389
00:34:57,800 --> 00:34:59,660
he will make his move against you.

390
00:35:05,630 --> 00:35:06,360
Of course,

391
00:35:07,200 --> 00:35:08,500
this is your business.

392
00:35:09,590 --> 00:35:11,450
It's up to you to decide what to do.

393
00:35:12,510 --> 00:35:14,310
But I still want to say one thing.

394
00:35:14,710 --> 00:35:17,800
Ma Derong has offended
countless people in Nanping.

395
00:35:18,740 --> 00:35:21,200
Many have tried
to bring him down in the past,

396
00:35:21,210 --> 00:35:22,870
but no one has ever succeeded.

397
00:35:24,630 --> 00:35:26,030
If you trust me,

398
00:35:27,630 --> 00:35:29,360
you can give the evidence to me.

399
00:35:30,820 --> 00:35:32,010
I am his secretary.

400
00:35:32,350 --> 00:35:33,590
I know what to do.

401
00:35:37,820 --> 00:35:40,020
You were right about one thing just now.

402
00:35:41,670 --> 00:35:43,070
This is my own business.

403
00:35:44,030 --> 00:35:45,290
I'll handle it myself.

404
00:35:47,630 --> 00:35:49,430
It's natural you don't trust me.

405
00:35:51,030 --> 00:35:52,230
I just hope

406
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:55,680
you'll think it over.

407
00:36:00,230 --> 00:36:01,480
If you think it through,

408
00:36:01,480 --> 00:36:02,920
you can call me anytime.

409
00:36:08,550 --> 00:36:10,750
Xia Xue has a prenatal checkup tomorrow

410
00:36:11,680 --> 00:36:13,740
at Nanping International Hospital.

411
00:36:37,230 --> 00:36:40,430
[Hou Jun, Nanping Xijiang Shipyard]

412
00:36:43,630 --> 00:36:47,550
♪ Let this farewell ♪

413
00:36:49,420 --> 00:36:52,620
♪ Freeze one thought ♪

414
00:36:53,970 --> 00:36:56,720
♪ In a fleeting instant ♪

415
00:36:58,970 --> 00:37:02,780
♪ The vacuum spreads ♪

416
00:37:04,370 --> 00:37:09,620
♪ Before the mist fades away ♪

417
00:37:12,890 --> 00:37:15,180
♪ A passing wind ♪

418
00:37:16,830 --> 00:37:21,260
♪ Reminds me to say goodbye ♪

419
00:37:22,810 --> 00:37:25,300
♪ Leave a single tear ♪

420
00:37:27,080 --> 00:37:31,350
♪ For time to tend ♪

421
00:37:33,240 --> 00:37:35,690
♪ Those lives that crossed ours ♪

422
00:37:37,100 --> 00:37:42,600
♪ Do you still remember ♪

423
00:37:44,720 --> 00:37:49,710
♪ Everything from before ♪

424
00:38:05,190 --> 00:38:09,590
[OB-GYN Clinic]

425
00:38:09,590 --> 00:38:10,670
I've

426
00:38:11,400 --> 00:38:13,130
made many decisions in my life,

427
00:38:19,030 --> 00:38:20,760
but never one like today,

428
00:38:21,510 --> 00:38:23,910
one that makes me keep questioning myself—

429
00:38:24,550 --> 00:38:25,860
Because you are

430
00:38:26,980 --> 00:38:28,440
the best girl in the world.

431
00:38:28,600 --> 00:38:31,180
♪ A passing wind ♪

432
00:38:32,490 --> 00:38:37,360
♪ Reminds me to say goodbye ♪

433
00:38:39,100 --> 00:38:41,530
♪ Leave a single tear ♪

434
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:47,480
♪ For time to tend ♪

435
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:51,510
♪ Those lives that crossed ours ♪

436
00:38:52,660 --> 00:38:58,780
♪ Do you still remember ♪

437
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:07,600
♪ Everything from before ♪

438
00:39:11,150 --> 00:39:17,320
♪ Everything ends today, goodbye ♪
